---
layout: article
pageable: true
---
%h2
  Archive for
  - case page_type
  - when 'day'
    = Date.new(year, month, day).strftime('%b %e %Y')
  - when 'month'
    = Date.new(year, month, 1).strftime('%b %Y')
  - when 'year'
    = year

- page_articles.each_with_index do |article, i|
  .row
    .span2.muted= article.date.strftime('%b %e %Y')
    .span10= link_to article.title, article